              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Image - 3 columns -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-3">
            <img
              src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2021/09/16/03/16/farmers-6628187_1280.jpg"
              alt="Smart farming"
              class="rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-full h-[600px] object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AI in Farming Section -->
        <div class="py-16 space-y-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">
            Why AI in Agriculture?
          </h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
              <div class="text-green-600 mb-4">
                <i data-feather="bar-chart-2" class="h-8 w-8"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Data-Driven Decisions</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Make informed decisions based on real-time data analytics and
                predictive modeling for better crop management.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
              <div class="text-green-600 mb-4">
                <i data-feather="droplet" class="h-8 w-8"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Resource Optimization</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Optimize water usage, fertilizer application, and other
                resources through smart monitoring systems.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
              <div class="text-green-600 mb-4">
                <i data-feather="trending-up" class="h-8 w-8"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Yield Prediction</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Accurately predict crop yields and optimize harvest timing using
                advanced machine learning algorithms.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
