                info@smartfarming.ai
              </p>
              <p class="flex items-center">
                <i data-feather="phone" class="h-4 w-4 mr-2"></i>
                +1 (555) 123-4567
              </p>
              <p class="flex items-center">
                <i data-feather="map-pin" class="h-4 w-4 mr-2"></i>
                123 AgTech Valley, CA 94025
              </p>
            </div>
